{"tid":823973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向中央表達行政長官應付颱風問題有冇用？","createTime":"2018-09-17T02:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T02:18:07.000Z","uid":59195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2fc52fa267defe90f45cb0233314ce6512626ff","tid":823973,"uid":59195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:18:07.000Z","msg":"作為港人，有責任對政府施政發表意見。<br />\n尋日打完個咁犀利既風，有人發文話舒一口氣但就無實質工作。佢舒完一口氣，大家喺佢個facebook講咩佢都唔會理，倒不如搵佢上司仲好<br />\n<br />\n上網搵到條link，係俾中國政府國民反映遇到既情況。但係要登記要有大陸電話卡要有大陸身分證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://liuyan.www.gov.cn/zwfwjbts/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliuyan.www.gov.cn%2Fzwfwjbts%2Findex.htm&d=KPPkmUstXgKNlaWvbQeyJrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4a2e6531\" target=\"_blank\">https://liuyan.www.gov.cn/zwfwjbts/index.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n但係，網頁上提供一個電郵係俾人send附件<br />\nsjhlanmuzu@mail.gov.cn<br />\n呢個或者係最簡單直接既方法<br />\n<br />\n有個留言系統叫向總理說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Direct inbox 習總理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但同上面一樣要有大陸身分證註冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/hudong/xzlwh.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fhudong%2Fxzlwh.htm&d=KPPkmUstXgKNlaWvbQeyJrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=35c49697\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.cn/hudong/xzlwh.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n退而求其次，中國政府微博，可以隨時留言。有微博戶口簡單得多<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/u/5000609535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fu%2F5000609535&d=KPPkmUstXgKNlaWvbQeyJrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=545abb21\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/u/5000609535</a><br />\n<br />\n至於香港中聯辦就只有聯絡電話，未知可唔可以表達意見<br />\n<br />\n除左上面既方法，仲有咩途徑向中央表達意見呢？"}]}